data.description: A beautiful 2BR 2BA townhome overlooking Gull Lake and gorgeous sunsets. Located across from the public access. Main floor amenities include spacious living and dining area, kitchen, 1/2 bath and a 3 season porch with cedar T&G, upper level boasts 2 BR's and a full walk through bath, basement has tuck under garage, storage, and laundry/utility room.
